      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know what the point is anymore. the doctors just keep saying \"manage the pain\" but it's not even pain anymore, it's just... this constant, heavy weight that never lets up. i'm so tired of fighting a body that's basically turned against me. it feels like i'm just prolonging a nightmare at this point.",
